<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Ry olo-mahantra
 Mihainoa izao !
 Saino tsara ny teny
 Izay lazaina aminao ;
 Ry olo-mahantra !
 Modia, modia,

[V2]
 Fa ela dia ela
 Hianao no nania,
 Tsy nahita ny tsara,
 Tsy nahazo ny soa ;
 Ry olo-mahantra ..sns.

[V3]
 Tsy misy mpiantra
 Mba hitsinjo anao
 Afa-tsy ny Mpamonjy,
 Izay mitady anao ;
 Ry olo-mahantra ..sns.

[V4]
 Tsarovy ny Rainao
 Malahelo anao
 Ka miandry tokoa
 Hampandroso anao ;
 Ry olo-mahantra ..sns.</lyrics>
<title>Ry olo-mahantra FFPM363</title>
<hymn_number>363</hymn_number>
<author>W.H. Doane</author>
</song>